;&lt;h2&gt;Start Here&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Read this first. This portal documents a Microsoft 365 Personal Cloud Lab built in tenant &lt;strong&gt;jeremyfontenot.online&lt;/strong&gt; using Microsoft 365 Business Premium. All configuration performed with PowerShell (Graph, Exchange Online, Teams).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Configuration Summary&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Tenant&amp;#58; &lt;code&gt;jeremyfontenot.online&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;License&amp;#58; Microsoft 365 Business Premium&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Admin&amp;#58; &lt;code&gt;jeremy.fontenot@jeremyfontenot.online&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Automation&amp;#58; Graph PowerShell, Exchange Online PowerShell, Teams PowerShell&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;PowerShell Commands Used&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-powershell&quot;&gt;
Connect-MgGraph -Scopes &#39;User.Read.All&#39;,&#39;Directory.Read.All&#39;,&#39;Policy.Read.All&#39;
Connect-ExchangeOnline
Connect-MicrosoftTeams
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Validation Steps&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Confirm access to all pages via top navigation.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Open each section to review configuration and validation steps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
